description:
Throw a storm of sharp pencils! Hits for 10 damage.
Zombies hate school supplies, especially airborne ones.
name: spell0.Pencil Barrage

description:
Zombies freeze up from a surprise test. Deals √(your 
health) damage. The healthier you are, the harder it is
name: spell1.Pop Quiz Panic

description:
Powered by playground energy! Deals 2× your current 
health. The more you bounce, the harder you hit.
name: spell2.Jump Rope Jab

description:
Fueled by apples and string cheese. Deals starting health 
+ 30 damage. Snack strong, slam harder!
name: spell3.Healthy Snack Slam

description:
Copies their strength! Deals half of the monster’s 
health. Works best when fighting the big scary ones.
name: spell4.Mirror Match

description:
Only for the fittest. Deals 1.5× starting health. Those 
laps weren’t for nothing—now make the zombies sweat.
name: spell5.PE Final Exam

description:
Fires concentrated boredom! Deals 90% of monster’s health.
Leaves them hanging on, just like after-school punishment.
name: spell6.Detention Ray

description:
You showed up every day—now show off! Deals starting health 
+ 80% of monster’s health. Extra credit for surviving clean.
name: spell7.Perfect Attendance Blast

description:
Unleash hallway chaos! Deals 95% of monster’s health 
+ 1.1× your health. Almost too strong for one spell to handle.
name: spell8. Hall Pass Havoc

description:
Summon the final authority! Instantly destroys one 
monster—no excuses, no mercy, and absolutely no permission slips required.
name: spell9.Principal’s Wrath

description:
Removes all status ailments.
Cannot revive a someone from being dead.
name: Dispel Herb

description: Restores HP and MP by half.
name: Miracle Drop

description:
Halves the number of enemies you will encounter
for a while.
name: Encounter Decreaser

description:
Increases items and money gained from battle for
a while.
name: Drop Increaser
